- Line 20 → line 21: used inside `printStackTrace(...)`. That is an **Argument** propagation to `printStackTrace`.
- No other assignments: `PrintWriter` is not assigned to any local variable (e.g., no `PrintWriter pw = new PrintWriter(...)`), so no aliasing.
